WEBVTT

00:01.734 --> 00:04.470
        Cheers <i>is filmed</i>        
 <i>before a live studio audience.</i> 

00:04.537 --> 00:06.739
             Woody.             

00:07.974 --> 00:09.641
I hear that you and Kelly       

00:09.709 --> 00:12.011
are having a hard time          
getting a wedding ring.         

00:12.078 --> 00:13.345
      That's right, Carla.      

00:13.413 --> 00:14.713
They're pretty expensive,       
        you know.               

00:14.781 --> 00:16.114
Yeah. That's                    
what I thought.                 

00:16.181 --> 00:18.717
And you know, I'm not           
gonna be able to afford         

00:18.785 --> 00:20.986
to get you kids the kind        
of present you really deserve,  

00:21.054 --> 00:22.788
so, on the way                  
over here                       

00:22.856 --> 00:26.025
I stopped by my bank,           
and, uh,                        

00:26.092 --> 00:28.494
I took this out                 
of my safety deposit box.       

00:28.561 --> 00:30.529
      Oh, Carla, that's a beaut!

00:30.597 --> 00:32.164
Yeah, I know.                   

00:32.232 --> 00:33.332
It's solid silver.              

00:33.400 --> 00:35.100
It's been in my family          
for years.                      

00:35.168 --> 00:37.603
My great uncle Amerigo          

00:37.671 --> 00:39.438
gave it to my                   
great aunt Sophia,              

00:39.506 --> 00:42.307
and then I was gonna give it    
to my youngest girl,            

00:42.375 --> 00:46.045
but she inherited               
the Tortelli knuckles.          

00:46.112 --> 00:47.980
              Oh, Carla, I could
                  never take it.

00:48.048 --> 00:50.282
Oh, Woody,                      
I-I want you to have it.        

00:50.350 --> 00:52.518
        Well, at least let me   
      give you something for it.

00:52.585 --> 00:53.886
    I have $500 in my budget.   

00:53.953 --> 00:56.989
Well, if it makes you           
feel better.                    

00:57.057 --> 00:59.058
                 Well, you know,
                the thing is,   

00:59.125 --> 01:01.527
                uh, Kelly really
                prefers gold.   

01:01.594 --> 01:02.928
        Oh.                     

01:02.996 --> 01:05.364
Well, I got it                  
in gold, too.                   

01:05.432 --> 01:07.700
                    Perfect.    

01:07.767 --> 01:09.635
Hey, does she need              
any earrings?                   

01:12.405 --> 01:14.340
      (theme song begins)       

